headline: Fifth Third Private Bank Recognized as Best Private Bank by Global Finance for Sixth Consecutive Year
summary: CINCINNATI, January 07, 2025--Fifth Third Private Bank, a division of Fifth Third Bank (NASDAQ: FITB), was named as a Best Private Bank (US, Regional) for the sixth consecutive year. In addition, the Private Bank was named Best Private Bank for Entrepreneurs (Globally) for the second year. The honors were announced by Global Finance for the 2025 World’s Best Private Bank Awards.
